    "World Gazetteer is a point theme representing the locations and proper names for map features around the world. The gazetteer includes attribute and annotation name information from various layers of the Digital Chart of the World. Attribute information includes the name, country category and description of the features. This dataset is a part of the 2008 ESRI Data and Maps Collection."
